        <detaileddescription>
<para>Cleans up the <ref refid="classBULKCC_1_1Controller" kindref="compound">Controller</ref>. Note: Does NOT automatically clean or erase any stacks or objects. You must call <ref refid="classBULKCC_1_1Controller_1aecc8d782c6c028ee173cb8b4c45e9782" kindref="member">erase()</ref> or <ref refid="classBULKCC_1_1Controller_1a9207ad31cc64c35e57067ad2d36a38f6" kindref="member">clean()</ref> on any active stacks before destroying the <ref refid="classBULKCC_1_1Controller" kindref="compound">Controller</ref>.</para>
